 “It was sad to not be invited to share a stage with Grammy Award-winning US Rapper T.I. in SA but now I'm happy to represent us in America!” tweets Kwesta.  The South African rapper Kwesta is heading back to the US for the homecoming finale of T.I's Hustle Gang Tour this weekend in Atlanta, Georgia. Kwesta recently headlined the international SXSW festival in Texas. The Ngud' hitmaker was hailed an "International Hyena" by Sway Calloway during an interview on his radio show. Kwesta bagged gongs for best male artist of the year, best rap album, highest airplay and best collaboration for his album Dakar at the South African Music Awards last month. Emtee strikes Gold  Tickets are available on hustlegangtour.com. IOL